01:14:32,301 --> 01:14:36,238
但我不是他一点也不感到羞愧。弹孔在他的面前。
But I ain't ashamed of him nohow. Bullet holes are in the front of him.

759
01:14:36,372 --> 01:14:38,534
所有这些轻人从点就是这样。
All those youngsters from the Point are like that.

760
01:14:38,642 --> 01:14:40,007
他们必须学习。
They got to learn.

761
01:14:40,209 --> 01:14:42,303
他们学习的部分,部分原因是他们死。
Partly they learn, partly they die.

762
01:14:42,512 --> 01:14:44,411
但是我得浮我坚持和你一样。
But I gotta float my stick same as you.

763
01:14:44,514 --> 01:14:47,176
我从来没见过其中一个我不得不感到羞耻。
I never saw one of them I had to be ashamed of.

764
01:15:18,013 --> 01:15:19,913
加入和继续前进。
Join in and keep moving.

765
01:15:22,518 --> 01:15:24,383
继续下去,那里!
Move it along, there!

766
01:15:24,787 --> 01:15:26,015
快点!
Hurry up!

767
01:15:33,362 --> 01:15:35,523
来,沿着这里!
Come on, move along here!

768
01:15:58,754 --> 01:16:00,346
来吧,快点。
Come on, hurry it up.

769
01:16:14,636 --> 01:16:16,297
圆的马车!
Circle the wagons!

770
01:16:19,040 --> 01:16:20,405
轮着她。
Wheel her around.

771
01:16:25,146 --> 01:16:26,808
坚持住!
Hold on!

772
01:16:53,141 --> 01:16:56,008
呆在车上。让大家在马车。
Stay in the wagon. Keep everybody in the wagons.

773
01:16:56,111 --> 01:16:57,408
和不放松。
And don't unhitch.

774
01:17:26,774 --> 01:17:28,002
本州!
Hondo!

775
01:17:28,676 --> 01:17:31,873
所有这些圆的做的是保护马。我们得把一些马车了。
All this circle's doing is protect the horses. We gotta turn some wagons over.

776
01:17:31,979 --> 01:17:34,448
和呆在这儿吗?这就是他们的期望。
And stay here? That's what they expect.

777
01:17:34,582 --> 01:17:35,981
我们必须做他们不期望。
We gotta do what they don't expect.

778
01:17:36,082 --> 01:17:38,744
这就是为什么所有的重型火炮的在布法罗的马车。
That's why all the heavy artillery's in Buffalo's wagon.

779
01:17:38,853 --> 01:17:40,320
水牛!
Buffalo!

780
01:17:42,957 --> 01:17:46,483
中尉,趴下。你准备好了,迷吗?
Lieutenant, get down. Are you ready, Buff?

781
01:17:46,594 --> 01:17:49,119
- 我出生做好准备。 - 走吧。
- I was born ready. - Let's go.

782
01:18:55,863 --> 01:18:57,420
圆的马车。
Circle the wagons.

783
01:18:58,164 --> 01:18:59,131
靠近。
Close up.

784
01:19:44,044 --> 01:19:45,671
呆下来!
Stay down!

785
01:19:45,779 --> 01:19:46,837
警官!
Sergeant!

786
01:20:09,602 --> 01:20:13,300
- 我不想是一个Apache,妈妈。-现在,你安静点。
- I don't want to be an Apache, Mama. - Now, you be quiet.

787
01:20:13,406 --> 01:20:16,500
我们要摆脱所有的权利。现在,帮助我,快点。
We're going to get out all right. Now, help me, hurry.

788
01:20:26,352 --> 01:20:30,448
- 准备好了再一次,迷吗? - 我告诉你,我出生做好准备。
- Ready again, Buff? - As I told you, I was born ready.

789
01:21:08,694 --> 01:21:09,922
把我你的刀。
Throw me your knife.

790
01:21:20,439 --> 01:21:22,600
滚开!
Get out of here!

791
01:22:30,308 --> 01:22:31,639
好吧,本州!
All right, Hondo!

792
01:22:34,078 --> 01:22:35,375
他们不遵循。
They're not following.

793
01:22:35,480 --> 01:22:37,880
领导人的死。他们会举行祈祷仪式,选择一个新的。
Leader's dead. They'll powwow and pick a new one.

794
01:22:37,983 --> 01:22:41,782
- 我们摆脱麻烦如果我们赶快。 - 我要去开车吗?
- We're out of trouble if we get a move on. - And am I going to get to drive?

795
01:22:41,887 --> 01:22:45,379
在我们到达圣迪马斯,你会成为一个顶级卡车驾驶员,儿子。
Before we get to San Dimas, you'll be a top teamster, son.

796
01:22:49,427 --> 01:22:51,362
- 你好,中尉? - 好,谢谢你。
- How are you, Lieutenant? - Fine, thanks to you.

797
01:22:51,462 --> 01:22:55,489
和你都是正确的,由于伦尼。他射,印度经常你的背部。
And you're all right, thanks to Lennie. He shot that Indian offen your back.

798
01:22:55,734 --> 01:22:57,428
- 谢谢。 - 与你的步枪。
- Thanks. - With your rifle.

799
01:22:57,702 --> 01:22:59,033
这是他的。
It's his.

800
01:22:59,337 --> 01:23:02,204
看起来不像我们需要它今天多。
Don't look like we'll be needing it much more today.

801
01:23:05,276 --> 01:23:08,473
一般骗子在一个月内将在这里有一个很大的力。
General Crook will be here within a month with a large force.

802
01:23:08,613 --> 01:23:11,878
- 这将结束的Apache。 - 是的。
- That'll be the end of the Apache. - Yeah.

803
01:23:13,017 --> 01:23:14,507
结束一种生活方式。
End of a way of life.

804
01:23:15,620 --> 01:23:17,610
太糟糕了,这是一个好方法。
Too bad, it's a good way.

805
01:23:18,022 --> 01:23:20,148
马车前进!
Wagons forward!


